{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I had experiences, you know, when we had a chance sometimes to go to a shower and we had a door opening and a thousand people tried to go through at the same time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you sort of get lifted up, you know, and if you're dropped, you're trampled to death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I said, I don't ever want to be in a line ever again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So-- and I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't have the strength to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was very fortunate, because many of those that did get there, they got a big pot full of stew, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They wolfed it down, you know, and many thousands, they just dropped like flies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They-- they died right on the spot, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because they could not take this food in their belly, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were not used to food for a whole year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And our system was completely shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so somebody gave me one bite of the stew, and I had this one bite and I just about brought up my whole insides, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the Americans realized that, you know, we cannot handle this food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know how we're-- how they were going to look after these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought, give them food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was ironic, you know, that, you know, we died without-- for lack of food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now that they gave us food, you know, that killed us, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they cut this food out, and they gave us crackers and some powdered milk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the medical-- the medical units came up, you know, from the army, you know, the-- and they had to start to look after us.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
